    "body": "I think you have encountered a regression of Chromium. It works in old versions of NW.js and Electron because they are using old versions of Chromium.\n\nThis is essentially a bug of Chromium, and I suggest reporting it to Chromium's issues list instead, I'm closing this because we are unable to fix it on Electron's side.\n"
